I'm having trouble to undestand what's wrong with this piece of code, psalm crashes with an "`Unexpected LHS of property`" exception. Does LHS stand for "Left Hand Side" ? If so, what's wrong in using get_class?

```php
private function hasAttachmentOfGivenType(string $attachment_type): bool
{
        $attachments = $this->getAttachments();

        if (empty($attachments)) {
            return false;
        }

        foreach ($attachments as $attachment) {
            if (is_object($attachment) && get_class($attachment) === $attachment_type) {
                return true;
            }
        }
        
        return false;
}
```

